Cell["\<\
The inner product is computed by contracting all tensor indices.\
\>", "Notes",
 CellID->8763854,ExpressionUUID->"a463a56d-89cb-1c49-b37f-6d588269b472"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[
  TemplateBox[{
    Cell[
     TextData["TensorTrainInnerProduct"]], 
    "paclet:RubenRanval/TensorTrainTools/ref/TensorTrainInnerProduct", 
    "RubenRanval Package Symbol"},
   "PackageLink",
   BaseStyle->"InlineFormula"]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "0c420e8b-a973-8d46-b680-8c6c214d4bc8"],
 " is conjugate-linear in the first argument and linear in the second. For \
real tensor trains this coincides with the plain Euclidean inner product."
}], "Notes",
 CellID->473134335,ExpressionUUID->"74611537-8217-c944-afbc-be7cd1a27885"],

